<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">Good Afternoon Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">Thank you for your patience,
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">I have completed my review of the outstanding payments on you=
r contents claim and arrange payment of the next $5,000 for temporary accom=
modation.&nbsp; Please confirm if this (and
 future temporary accommodation payments) can be made into the same account=
 as the previous ones. &nbsp;Once I receive confirmation I will arrange pay=
ment urgently, with this usually being processed within 3 =E2=80=93 5 busin=
ess days.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">I have also noted that you provided costs for vet fees.&nbsp;=
 These would not be able to be reimbursed as the vet fees are not covered b=
y the policy if your pet is injured in an
 accident with a motor vehicle.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">I can see Zach has already advised you that the water rates w=
ould not be able to be reimbursed.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">I also am happy to confirm that future payments for temporary=
 accommodation will be acted upon far more promptly, I recommend sending th=
ese to costs to the claims email address,
 and copying me into it as well.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">Please let me know if you have any further questions.<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ligatures:standa=
rdcontextual">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
